node.text:
The latest fatality — identified as Case 128 — is the third #covid19 death in four days. The deceased was a family member of Case 125, who is linked to the Safra Jurong cluster.⁣
⁣
Earlier, on Tuesday (April 14) the Ministry of Health announced 334 new cases of Covid-19, bringing the total number of confirmed infections in Singapore to 3,252.⁣
⁣
#linkinbio for the full report⁣
